                <mxCell id="ragParse" value="core.llm.parse_command_rag()&#xa;&#xa;LMSTUDIO_URL · LMSTUDIO_MODEL&#xa;LMSTUDIO_TEMPERATURE · LMSTUDIO_NO_THINK&#xa;LMSTUDIO_TIMEOUT · LMSTUDIO_API_KEY&#xa;Prompt: prompts.yaml::rag_parser&#xa;Candidates injected (friendly_name / actions / meta)&#xa;LLM_HISTORY_SIZE history injected&#xa;Validates entity_id against candidate set&#xa;needs_fallback always allowed&#xa;MAX_ACTIONS_PER_COMMAND cap&#xa;&#xa;Returns:&#xa;  { reply, actions[], clarification_question? }&#xa;If the LLM is unsure it picks the right candidate(s)&#xa;it may emit clarification_question and no actions." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;align=left;fontSize=11;" parent="coreLane" vertex="1">
