                <mxCell id="tgFmt" value="handlers._format_reply(result)&#xa;&#xa;&#39;no_match&#39; + reply → &#39;💬 reply&#39;&#xa;known error → German message from _ERROR_MESSAGES&#xa;else: reply text + ✅/❌ per executed action&#xa;       + ⚠️ per ignored (limit) action&#xa;Sent via update.message.reply_text(parse_mode=&#39;Markdown&#39;)&#xa;Falls back to plain text if Markdown fails." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;fontSize=11;" parent="outLane" vertex="1">
