                <mxCell id="gwPush" value="GATEWAY_TELEGRAM_PUSH=true ?&#xa;&#xa;_telegram_push() — sends formatted&#xa;receipt to MY_CHAT_ID via BOT_TOKEN.&#xa;Includes transcript, reply, ✅/❌ actions, error.&#xa;Runs in addition to the device response." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;fontSize=11;" parent="outLane" vertex="1">
